parameters.name: Celt
parameters.description: Number of sketch hatches for this sketch hatch enumeration

parameters.name: Rgelt
parameters.description: Pointer to an array of sketch hatches of size Celt

parameters.name: PceltFetched
parameters.description: Pointer to the number of sketch hatches returned from the list; this value can be less than celt if you ask for more SketchHatch objects than exist, or it can be NULL if no more SketchHatch objects exist
